  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Idle\n    Idle --> Processing : start\n    Processing --> Success : complete\n    Processing --> Error : fail\n    Error --> Idle : reset\n    Success --> Idle : restart\n    Success --> [*] : finish\n",
