      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，初始状态指向Idle，Idle通过start事件转到Processing。那Processing之后有哪些分支？是成功和失败两种情况吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Success",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Processing执行complete就进入Success，如果fail则进入Error状态。这两个分支都要画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "complete",
        "fail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经加上了Processing到Success的complete转换，以及Processing到Error的fail转换。接下来Error和Success怎么流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "complete",
        "fail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Error状态需要能reset回Idle重新来，Success则可以restart回Idle，或者finish到终止状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Success",
        "reset",
        "restart",
        "finish",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Error通过reset回到Idle，Success有两条出路——restart回Idle，finish到终止状态。这样整个流程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Success",
        "reset",
        "restart",
        "finish",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样用户既能从成功状态重新开始新任务，也能直接结束整个流程。状态机就这些元素，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
